title: Recording Incompetence?
selftext:
Surprising the Spanish people are also not kept in trauma center or, they planning to taking a break and let police do the work.

What is this weird behaviour?
comments: These people seem to live on social media more than in real life.
This is a pic from before, look at their faces, there are no stitches on Vincents lips and no multiple bruises on their face.
